203
00:13:50,679 --> 00:13:51,879
…dia muncul lagi.

204
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,039
Mari.

205
00:14:07,399 --> 00:14:08,159
Pegang baik-baik.

206
00:14:09,759 --> 00:14:10,360
